ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString:
If(
    commitedRadioC.Selected.Value = 'Commited (Leads)'.Yes && Self.Selected.Value = "80-100",
    Notify(
        "Probability should be 80-100 if the lead is committed",
        NotificationType.Success,
        2000
    ),
    commitedRadioC.Selected.Value = 'Commited (Leads)'.No && Self.Selected.Value = "80-100",
    Notify(
        "Probability cannot be 80-100 if the lead is not committed",
        NotificationType.Success,
        2000
    )
)
